This paper is about action recognition in videos using a spatio-temporal fusion network. Therefore, the most likely category is computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning and end-to-end training, which are common in machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also mentions the use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs), which are commonly used in multimedia (cs.MM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) research.
